GraphML test files created with various yWorks tools (yEd, yFiles for Java, yFiles for HTML),
organised into sub-folders by the exact tool version that wrote them.

ddot.it/this ..format.. format:graphml
ddot.it/this ..created with.. yWorks tools (yEd / yFiles)

NOTE on license: yWorks tools do not claim copyright over the GraphML they emit; rights to a
file's content belong to whoever authored the graph. Most files here are synthetic test graphs
authored within this project (treat as public domain unless otherwise stated). A few depict
third-party content and inherit that content's situation -- see each folder's meta.ddot or
per-file .ddot sidecars:
  yed-3.12.2/      mixed: synthetic graphs + Google Guava class graph (Apache-2.0) + a Goobi
                   topology diagram; licenses differ per file, so each file has its own .ddot sidecar
  yed-3.14.3/      synthetic sample graphs
  yed-3.18.0.2/    a single large unlabeled graph
  yfiles-html-3.0.0.3/  SVG-node samples (one triggers a SAX parser bug)
  yfiles-java-2.8/ a French "classements" configuration diagram (third-party origin)
